<br />\n起碼1個鐘多d先返到去<br />\n<br />\n最嬲係我係總站等車,佢老味on99<br />\n<br />\n1架車都無,我返九半,7半等車,佢老味閪8點半先有1架車返黎都夠膽死<br />\n<br />\n出到香港仔隧道口又要塞,塞到紅隧又塞<br />\n<br />\n第日醒d早少少去到等車,佢老味又遲返我早起既時間先黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3956a8ed92693722dde174e8dee9a2f55c87a2","tid":38560,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住新界西嘅去中環同九龍灣都係咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九龍東係就係多咗工廈<br />\n但交通配套一樣垃圾個度弊呢<br />\n晚晚觀塘線同觀塘道塞死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n觀塘是垃圾地方，九龍收工返觀塘要個半鐘</blockquote><br />\n觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食屎啦，日撚日都塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住九龍平時返放工半個鐘，一要走九龍灣上堂就仆街！等6-7架巴士都上唔撚到，又塞到仆街，真係鬼地方</blockquote><br />\n入龍翔道/清水灣道、九龍灣地鐵站、開源道呢三個係死位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de5686847b8c4e0905958a2e4714ec87c7751e2","tid":38560,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以新商業區的發展好主要，起動九龍東之後，觀塘到九龍灣多左好多商廈，方便左九龍、將軍澳人返工。</blockquote><br />\n新界西冇希望</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住新界西嘅去中環同九龍灣都係咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九龍東係就係多咗工廈<br />\n但交通配套一樣垃圾個度弊呢<br />\n晚晚觀塘線同觀塘道塞死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天水圍番九龍東慘過番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7b71e23892384b137d2cd55439f70e6ab08c66","tid":38560,"uid":56993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:15:11.000Z","msg":"來回三個鐘或以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/